channel.title: Help With Items (Could Be Rewarded)
channel.description:
Okay im having trouble with my server.Along time ago with the same source, I had my full d helm and skill capes working in the right slots and all.But know when i spawn them there not the items i wanted there tool boxes. :mad:
Please help if you can. :)
The person who helps me solve this problem will get Co-Owner on my server.

item.title: Help With Items (Could Be Rewarded)
item.dc:creator: @_Patrick +Patrick
item.description:
@_Patrick wrote:

satesql:

Your both wrong, it seems like your using an incorrect cache for your client… Meaning the items you have now aren’t compatible with the client, so it turns the items into nulls meaning non existent…

Oh, haha I didn’t read his whole post. I read the top where it said it went to the wrong slot >.<, my mistake. Yeah, your cache needs to load it probably off Class8 (java) and it needs to load the modelID’s from the cache.
